plot: When a dangerous artifact is used to murder a close colleague in a plot involving revenge against Artie, Katie Logan, a Secret Service Agent from Pete's past, becomes embroiled in the case.

When someone uses artifacts from Artie's past to commit a series of murders, the team must fly to Russia to track down the killer. But things get more complicated when HG tracks them down and offers to help. Meanwhile, Claudia digs into Todd's past and finds some disturbing information.—Anonymous
